This project bundles and depends on third-party software.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
blinkpy
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A patched build of blinkpy (an unofficial Python library for Blink cameras) is
vendored in `vendor/` to handle Blink's current 2FA (HTTP 202) login flow.

